</head>
<body class="legal-page">
  <header class="legal-header"><a href="/" class="brand">SourcemAI</a></header>
  <main class="legal-main">
    <h1>Data Processing Addendum</h1>
    <p class="muted">Last updated: <%= lastUpdated %></p>
    <p>This Data Processing Addendum (DPA) forms part of your SourcemAI Terms of Service and applies when SourcemAI processes personal data on your behalf in connection with the service.</p>
    <h2>1. Roles</h2><p>You are the Controller. SourcemAI is the Processor for the personal data you upload or sync.</p>
    <h2>2. Processing details</h2><p>Categories of data: contact names, business email addresses, job titles, employer (account) names, CRM activity timestamps. Purposes: surfacing ranked account recommendations to your sales team. Duration: while your account is active plus 30 days for export.</p>
    <h2>3. Subprocessors</h2><p>See the <a href="/subprocessors">subprocessor list</a>. We notify subscribers of new subprocessors with 30 days' notice.</p>
    <h2>4. Security</h2><p>Encryption at rest and in transit, least-privilege access, audit logging, breach notification within 72 hours.</p>
    <h2>5. International transfers</h2><p>Standard Contractual Clauses apply where data leaves the EEA / UK.</p>
    <h2>6. Returns &amp; deletion</h2><p>On termination, personal data is deleted within 30 days, except where retention is required by law.</p>
    <p class="footer-links"><a href="/">← Back to home</a></p>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
